title: #70 - Boogie2988 (Steven Williams)
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast Steven Williams better known as Boogie2988 returns to the studio for a heartfelt chat with Ethan and Hila. Together we discuss his weight loss surgery, divorce, YouTube content, VidCon, E3, and so much more! Boogie2988 is a vlogger and comedian and one of the longest lived channels on YouTube.
